title: IPC Standards (ipc- printed circuit board PCB standards )
description:
IPC Standards

here i have a few ipc standards documents and Reflow Soldering Processes Troubleshooting by   Ning-Cheng Lee.
most of these documents are outdated although the last editions have minor changes.

IPC-A-600G
IPC-A-610D En
IPC-A-610E-En
ipc-a-610dc-telecom-addendum
IPC-A-610D En
IPC-A-600G
IPC-7351B - Generic Requirements for Surface Mount Design and Land Pattern Standard
IPC-7526
IPC-2221-A
IPC-JEDEC J-STD-020C
IPC-JEDEC J-STD-033A 07.02
IPC-JST-033B
IPC TM650
plus: Reflow Soldering Processes Troubleshooting  Ning-Cheng Lee


i would be very pleased if some of these documents can help you in your education. but if you are working in design or manufacturing please buy the last versions cause it has changes, not many but enough to make a big mistake. i should be able to find more of the ipc standards or some guide-books if anyone is interested.
